### Variables
@id = {{createCarrera.response.body.data.id}}

### GET ALL CARRERAS
GET http://localhost:3000/api/carreras

### GET ONE CARRERA
GET http://localhost:3000/api/carreras/{{id}}

### POST - Crear nueva carrera
# @name createCarrera
POST http://localhost:3000/api/carreras
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Gran Premio de Australia",
    "start_date": "2024-03-15T10:00:00Z",
    "end_date": "2024-03-17T16:00:00Z",
    "temporada": 1,
    "circuito": 1,
    "sesiones": [1, 2]
}

### POST - Otra carrera de ejemplo
POST http://localhost:3000/api/carreras
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Gran Premio de Argentina",
    "start_date": "2027-06-18T10:00:00Z",
    "end_date": "2027-06-20T17:00:00Z",
    "temporada": "2027"
}

### PUT - Actualizar carrera completa
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/carreras/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Gran Premio de Bahréin",
    "start_date": "2024-03-15T09:00:00Z",
    "end_date": "2024-03-17T15:30:00Z",
    "temporada": "2024"
}

### PATCH - Actualizar carrera parcial (solo temporada)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/carreras/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Gran Premio de Bahréin"
}

### DELETE - Eliminar carrera
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/carreras/{{id}}

### GET ONE - Carrera específica (ID fijo para pruebas)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/carreras/2
